{
    "poem_title": "- LXVI - ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Francisco de La Torre",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Tirsis, la nave del cuidado Iolas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "hecha tablas, la vuelca el mar furioso;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "cuerpo muerto y espíritu penoso",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "le traen fiera Leucipe y fieras olas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tirsis, la nave del cuidado Iolas,\nhecha tablas, la vuelca el mar furioso;\ncuerpo muerto y espíritu penoso\nle traen fiera Leucipe y fieras olas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Dio mil voces al cielo y escondiolas",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+++--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "crudo cielo en el manto tenebroso",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "de la callada noche; y el rabioso",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "Bóreas le apresuró la muerte a solas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dio mil voces al cielo y escondiolas\ncrudo cielo en el manto tenebroso\nde la callada noche; y el rabioso\nBóreas le apresuró la muerte a solas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Salieron a la playa deseada",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "Lícidas y Damón, del mar echado;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "oyéronle, mas no le socorrieron.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Salieron a la playa deseada\nLícidas y Damón, del mar echado;\noyéronle, mas no le socorrieron."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "¡Ay, teme, Tirsis, la tormenta airada,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "que en el lugar donde otros perecieron,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "mal te pueden valer tus crudos hados!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¡Ay, teme, Tirsis, la tormenta airada,\nque en el lugar donde otros perecieron,\nmal te pueden valer tus crudos hados!"
        }
    ]
}